ure%20from%20anti-colonial%20movements%2C%20the%20U.S.%20signed%20treaties%20in%201977%20granting%20Panama%20control%20and%20full%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20canal%20zone%20and%20guaranteeing%20its%20permanent%20neutrality.%20These%20took%20effect%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202023%20and%202024%2C%20a%20severe%20drought%20aggravated%20by%20climate%20change%20lowered%20the%20level%20of%20lakes%20feeding%20the%20canal%2C%20forcing%20its%20administrator%20to%20restrict%20transits%20and%20vessel%20draft%2C%20which%20increased%20costs%20and%20waiting%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20passage%20restrictions%20were%20lifted%20late%20last%20year%2C%20but%20the%20waterway%20has%20not%20yet%20seen%20a%20full%20return%20of%20normal%20traffic%20as%20many%20shippers%2C%20especially%20bulk%20carriers%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20tankers%2C%20have%20continued%20taking%20alternative%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20CHINA'S%20INVOLVEMENT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20inaugural%20address%20last%20week%2C%20Trump%20repeated%20accusations%20he%20made%20following%20his%20election%20victory%20that%20Panama%20has%20ceded%20control%20of%20the%20canal%20to%20China.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20Chinese%20troops%20are%20stationed%20at%20the%20canal%2C%20without%20providing%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Panama's%20government%20and%20the%20Chinese%20government%20have%20rejected%20those%20assertions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECK%20Hutchison%20Holdings%2C%20a%20Hong%20Kong-based%20company%2C%20has%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20operated%20the%20ports%20of%20Balboa%20and%20Cristobal%20at%20the%20canal's%20Pacific%20and%20Atlantic%20entrances.%20The%20company%20is%20publicly%20listed%20and%20not%20financially%20tied%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20though%20Hong%20Kong%20firms%20are%20subject%20to%20government%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20U.S.%20firm%20SSA%20Marine%20operates%20the%20MIT%20port%20on%20the%20Atlantic%20coast%2C%20Taiwan's%20Evergreen%20Group%20operates%20another%20Atlantic%20port%20known%20as%20CCT%2C%20and%20Singapore's%20PSA%20International%20operates%20the%20Rodman%20port%20on%20the%20Pacific%20coast%2C%20according%20to%20company%20and%20government%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20economic%20influence%20has%20been%20growing%20in%20Latin%20America%2C%20fueling%20worries%20in%20Washington%20that%20the%20resource-rich%20region%20will%20tilt%20to%20Chinese%20interests%20rather%20than%20those%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanamanian%20President%20Jose%20Raul%20Mulino%20has%20asserted%20that%20the%20canal%20is%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20Panamanian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanama's%20authorities%20recently%20announced%20an%20audit%20on%20CK%20Hutchison's%20operated%20ports%2C%20saying%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20firm's%20compliance%20with%20concession%20agreements%20and%20whether%20it%20is%20adequately%20reporting%20its%20revenues%20and%20state%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECK%20Hutchison's%20local%20arm%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20Reuters%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20it%20has%20paid%20the%20state%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20during%20its%20concession%20and%20that%20its%20labor%20force%20is%2099.9%25%20Panamanian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDISPUTE%20OVER%20TOLLS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20complained%20that%20the%20fees%20charged%20to%20ships%20to%20use%20the%20canal%20are%20too%20high%2C%20and%20has%20accused%20Panama%20of%20levying%20unfair%20tariffs%20on%20U.S.%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerican%20ships%20are%20being%20severely%20overcharged%20and%20not%20treated%20fairly%20in%20any%20way%20and%20that%20includes%20the%20United%20States%20Navy%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20the%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20the%20fiscal%20years%20ended%20in%202020%20and%202023%2C%20the%20canal's%20toll%20revenue%20increased%20almost%2026%25%20to%20%243.35%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20its%20annual%20reports.%20In%20the%20fiscal%20year%20ended%20last%20September%2C%20the%20canal%20offset%20less%20vessel%20traffic%20with%20a%20water%20surcharge%2C%20which%20it%20combined%20with%20slot%20auctions%20that%20rose%20to%20as%20much%20as%20%244%20million%20per%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20canal's%20fees%20are%20not%20differentiated%20by%20a%20ship's%20flag%2C%20country%20of%20origin%2C%20or%20of%20destination.%20The%20United%20States%20does%20not%20have%20a%20relevant%20commercial%20fleet%20under%20its%20flag%2C%20and%20U.S.%20military%20ships%20enjoy%20priority%20of%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulino%20said%20the%20tariffs%20are%20carefully%20and%20transparently%20evaluated%20according%20to%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20shipping%20experts%20and%20cargo%20movers%2C%20tolling%20fee%20increases%20have%20been%20applied%20in%20recent%20years%20by%20other%20key%20waterways%20amid%20demand%20spikes%20and%20geopolitical%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT'S%20NEXT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20threat%20is%20already%20impacting%20Panama's%20debt%20rating.%20U.S.%20investment%20bank%20JPMorgan%20downgraded%20its%20recommendation%20on%20the%20country's%20bonds%20over%20threats%20to%20the%20canal%2C%20a%20key%20source%20of%20national%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20is%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20Panama%20between%20late%20January%20and%20early%20February%2C%20his%20first%20foreign%20visit%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmigration%20will%20be%20a%20focus%20of%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulino%2C%20who%20took%20office%20last%20year%2C%20has%20taken%20a%20harder%20line%20on%20migration%20than%20his%20predecessor%2C%20agreeing%20to%20U.S.-funded%20deportation%20flights%20from%20Panama%20and%20installing%20barbed%20wire%20at%20the%20Darien%20Gap%2C%20a%20dangerous%20jungle%20ro