's%20challenges.%20In%20response%20to%20criticism%20from%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20regarding%20the%20Liberal%20Party's%20damaging%20impact%20on%20the%20Canadian%20society%20and%20economy%2C%20Dhalla%20outlined%20her%20initiatives%20to%20address%20crime%2C%20housing%20and%20food%20prices%2C%20and%20taxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20she%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20competitive%20economy%20that%20supports%20businesses%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20young%20people.%20With%20her%20international%20experience%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20restore%20Canada's%20reputation%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20and%20build%20strong%20partnerships%20with%20other%20countries.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20important%20that%20we%20bring%20Canada%20back%20to%20the%20country%20that%20was%20very%20respected%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%20that%20we%20work%20with%20other%20countries%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20continue%20to%20build%20great%20partnerships%20and%20great%20relationships.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738064460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fsc99f5vo_ruby-dhalla-x_625x300_28_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-indian-origin-ruby-dhalla-on-race-to-become-canadas-next-prime-minister-7579035%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20self-made%20businesswoman%2C%20doctor%2C%20and%20three-time%20MP%2C%20Dhalla%20believes%20she%20has%20the%20experience%20to%20navigate%20Canada's%20challenges.%20Her%20slogan%2C%20'Canada's%20comeback%20starts%20now'%20reflects%20her%20commitment%20to%20addressing%20the%20country's%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Don't%20ask%2C%20don't%20tell%2C%20don't%20come%3A%20Trump%20bans%20transgender%20individuals%20from%20US%20military%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738064362000%2C%22visual%22%3