e%20Launch%20Vehicle%20F%2015%20(GSLV%20F-15)%20is%20being%20flown%20with%20a%20swadeshi%20or%20an%20indigenous%20cryogenic%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20complex%20technology%20to%20harness%20and%20now%20India%20has%20mastered%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Narayanan%20speaking%20to%20NDTV%20from%20the%20launch%20port%20after%20inspecting%20what%20he%20called%20was%20team%20ISRO's%20%26quot%3B100th%20beautiful%20baby%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20stood%20magnificently%20in%20the%20moonlight%20weighing%20nearly%20420%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20associate%20vehicle%20director%20for%20the%20GSLV%20D-5%2C%20ten%20years%20back%20when%20the%20first%20indigenously%20made%20cryogenic%20engine%20succeeded%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Narayanan%20recalling%20the%20January%205%2C%202014%20launch%2C%20adding%20it%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20fulfilling%20journey%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECryogenic%20engines%20pack%20the%20best%20punch%20to%20launch%20satellites%20in%20space.%20The%20fuel%20they%20use%20is%20liquid%20hydrogen%20and%20liquid%20oxygen%20and%20it%20was%20this%20technology%20that%20was%20denied%20to%20India%20by%20the%20then%20USSR%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Narayanan%2C%20then%20a%20young%20engineer%2C%20was%20drafted%20into%20the%20project%20to%20make%20an%20Indian%20cryogenic%20engine%20and%20after%2020%20years%20of%20active%20tinkering%2C%20ISRO%20did%20succeed%20and%20today%20all%20the%20heavier%20rockets%20launched%20by%20India%20use%20the%20Indian%20cryogenic%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20a%20divine%20blessing%20to%20have%20worked%20on%20cryogenic%20engines%20and%20it%20has%20been%20a%20very%20satisfying%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20had%20jitters%20about%20the%20one%20hundredth%20launch%2C%20Dr%20Narayanan%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20the%20launch%20will%20go%20off%20well%20since%20India%20has%20learnt%20from%20its%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20the%20ISRO%20had%20taken%20any%20special%20measures%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20one%20hundredth%20rocket%20launch%20does%20not%20fail%2C%20Dr%20S%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20Director%20of%20India's%20main%20rocket%20lab%20the%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%2C%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20as%20robust%20as%20previous%20one.%20Like%20any%20other%20launch.%20We%20make%20every%20launch%20robust%20to%20the%20best%20of%20our%20ability.%20It%20will%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20big%20rocket%20to%20liftoff%20from%20Sriharikota%20was%20the%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(SLV-3)%20on%20August%2010%2C%201979%2C%20and%20now%20nearly%2046%20years%20later%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%20is%20ready%20to%20hit%20a%20century.%20On%20the%20one%20hundredth%20launch%2C%20ISRO%20hopes%20to%20place%20in%20orbit%20a%20navigation%20satellite%20weighing%20nearly%202%2C000%20kilogramme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigation%20with%20Indian%20Constellation%20(NavIC)%20is%20India's%20independent%20regional%20navigation%20satellite%20system%20designed%20to%20provide%20accurate%20Position%2C%20Velocity%20and%20Timing%20(PVT)%20service%20to%20users%20in%20India%20as%20well%20as%20the%20region%20extending%20about%201%2C500%20km%20beyond%20the%20Indian%20landmass%2C%20which%20is%20its%20primary%20service%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaunch%20number%20one%20hundred%20is%20a%20historical%20milestone%20for%20ISRO%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Narayanan%2C%20adding%20that%20SLV-3%20could%20only%20carry%2040%20kilogramme%20to%20space%2C%20now%20India's%20own%20rockets%20can%20ferry%20up%20to%208%2C500%20kilogramme%20to%20space.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738063620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fa2r6akc8_isro-new_625x300_28_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.