0about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-mom-parent-regret-wait-have-kids-prioritize-career-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoosing%20my%20kids%20over%20my%20career%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Getting%20to%20raise%20my%20two%20sons%20was%20fulfilling%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20I%20could%20have%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20being%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20my%20boys'%20unconditional%20love%20was%20healing%20for%20me.%20It%20allowed%20parts%20of%20my%20character%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I%20had%20suppressed%20during%20my%20career%20%E2%80%94%20to%20flourish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20there%20was%20the%20hell%20that%20was%20potty%20training%2C%20the%20weeks%20of%20my%20life%20spent%20in%20the%20car%20on%20school%20runs%2C%20and%20every%20trip%20to%20the%20doctor's%20when%20they%20were%20hurting%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20help%20them.%20Then%2C%20there%20were%20the%20magical%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20company%2C%20I%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-children-taught-parent-prioritize-career-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebe%20a%20child%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stopping%20to%20look%20at%20a%20robin%20in%20a%20tree%20was%20never%20something%20I%20did%20pre-children%2C%20but%20when%20I%20heard%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20mommy%2C%20a%20robin!%26quot%3B%20the%20three%20of%20us%20halted%20and%20took%20a%20moment%20to%20enjoy%20this%20simple%20pleasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20the%20times%20during%20rush%20hour%20when%2C%20amid%20blasting%20horns%20and%20angry%20drivers%2C%20we'd%20listen%20to%20books%20on%20tape%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Secret%20Garden%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Penguin%20Who%20waned%20to%20Find%20Out%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20childhood%20classics%20that%20I'd%20missed%20out%20on%20in%20my%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20moved%20to%20tears%20as%20baby%20penguin%20was%20reunited%20with%20his%20mother.%20The%20tears%20eventually%20stopped%20after%20the%2018th%20rerun.%20However%2C%20moments%20like%20these%20made%20being%20a%20stay-at-home%20mom%20never%20feel%20like%20pulling%20the%20short%20straw%3B%20it%20felt%20like%20winning%20the%20lottery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0b420d4-1950-4e4a-956d-e4c10e973c36%5C%22%3EI%20couldn't%20go%20back%20to%20law%2C%20so%20I%20changed%20careers%20once%20my%20kids%20were%20more%20independent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20two%20boys%20are%2017%20and%2015%20now.%20We%20share%20a%20closeness%20that%20I%20believe%20only%20exists%20because%20I%20was%20there%20from%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222236%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angela%20Zaher%20stands%20with%20her%20two%20grown%20sons%20in%20front%20of%20a%20yellow%20food%20truck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679133822fcded5e9074429b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221677%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20feel%20a%20very%20close%20bond%20to%20my%20boys.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Angela%20Zaher%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20navigate%20the%20tricky%20teenage%20years%2C%20I%20know%20them%20on%20a%20deeper%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20stressing%20over%20exams%20to%20feeling%20self-conscious%20about%20acne%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20support%20and%20help%20them%20through%20these%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20they%20were%20old%20enough%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwish-i-could-give-child-more-independence-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20to%20school%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20started%20preparing%20for%20empty%20nest%20syndrome.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20too%20late%20to%20return%20to%20a%20legal%20career%20%E2%80%94%20the%20child%20in%20me%20had%20taken%20up%20residence%20and%20needed%20a%20channel%20for%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20pursued%20a%20new%20career%20in%20writing%2C%20and%20fortunat