52cc08567%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'll%20then%20make%20breakfast%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20make%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20same%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebreakfast%20every%20morning%2C%20which%20includes%20some%20protein%2C%20typically%20sausage%2C%20and%20blueberries%2C%20my%20favorite%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I'm%20getting%20breakfast%20ready%2C%20I%20jump%20into%20some%20emails.%20I'll%20call%20and%20text%20different%20departments%20to%20check%20up%20on%20things%20and%20talk%20to%20our%20Chief%20Commercial%20Officer%20or%20CFO.%20In%20between%2C%20I'll%20watch%20some%20news%20to%20understand%20what's%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20out%20a%20bit%20every%20morning%20with%20a%20trainer%20or%20on%20the%20elliptical%20while%20watching%20ESPN%20or%20CNBC.%20I'll%20shower%2C%20and%20then%20I'll%20hit%20the%20ground%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2748ea9-62b0-4036-a567-c107f1690eff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDepending%20on%20traffic%2C%20I%20leave%20home%20and%20get%20to%20the%20office%20between%208%3A30%20a.m.%20and%209%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20office%20in%20St.%20Louis%20and%20around%20the%20country.%20I%20like%20being%20in%20an%20office%20and%20around%20people%2C%20as%20I'm%20an%20auditory%20learner.%20I%20thrive%20on%20the%20energy%20and%20the%20varying%20numbers%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20I%20work%20better%20in%20an%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-hybrid-work-from-home-jobs-persisting-fewer-new-roles-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20house%20full%20of%20teenagers%20was%20not%20ideal.%20I%20realized%20I%20needed%20a%20separate%20workspace%20to%20do%20as%20much%20real%20work%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228460821a-2987-4211-b484-a85765a6752f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20I%20get%20to%20the%20office%2C%20I'm%20booked%20all%20day%20with%20an%20occasional%2015%20min%20gap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20a%20CEO%20or%20C-suite%20executive%2C%20your%20schedule%2C%20rhythm%2C%20and%20routines%20are%20monthly%20or%20quarterly%2C%20as%20no%20two%20days%20are%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20monthly%20routine%20around%20performance%20reviews%20with%20my%20teams.%20Then%2C%20I%20have%20quarterly%20routines%20around%20board%20meetings%2C%20earnings%2C%20and%20investor%20communications.%20Annually%2C%20there's%20a%20rhythm%20with%20industry%20events%20and%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20big%20routine%20guy%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20having%20routines%20is%20supercritical.%20My%20assistant%20and%20I%20started%20working%20on%20my%202025%20calendar%20last%20June%2C%20and%20by%20October%2C%20we'd%20been%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20locked%20and%20committed.%20I%20believe%20in%20trying%20to%20have%2070%25%20of%20a%20plan%20with%2030%25%20time%20adjustable%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea21ed5e-6d88-489c-b771-61f46035eba6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20leave%20the%20office%20or%20take%20a%20lunch%20break%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20protein%20bar%20at%2010%20a.m.%20and%20a%20banana%20at%2011%20a.m.%2C%20and%20I%20bring%20deli%20meat%2C%20lettuce%2C%20blueberries%2C%20and%20protein%20shakes%20to%20the%20office%20to%20snack%20on%20throughout%20the%20day.%20I'm%20difficult%20to%20work%20with%20if%20I've%20gone%20two%20hours%20or%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-spector-increase-fiber-plant-based-protein-sources-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20day%20consists%20of%20meetings%20and%20hands-on%20work%20with%20the%20team.%20I%20try%20not%20to%20over-mange%20our%20team%3B%20I%20let%20great%20people%20do%20what%20they're%20capable%20of%2C%20but%20I%20like%20to%20be%20on%20top%20of%20things%20and%20not%20be%20surprised.%20I%20think%20the%20more%20you%20micromanage%2C%20the%20more%20you%20lose%20the%20ability%20to%20adapt.%20You%20need%20to%20have%20a%20strong%2C%20empowered%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20a%20little%20on%20weekends%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20quick%20calls%20with%20my%20team%2C%20reviewing%20pre-reads%2C%20and%20always%20devoting%20time%20to%20reading%20business%20media%20for%20articles%20to%20share%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d10bcb74-71fd-4f65-b2e8-bedfaa70938d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20evenings%20vary%2C%20but%20they're%20pretty%20boring%20as%20an%20empty%20nester%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20now%20just%20my%20wife%20and%20I%2C%20as%20our%20kids%20have%20left%20home%20for%20their%20adult%20lives.%20I%20build%20in%20nights%20out%20and%20protect%20vacations%20relentlessly%2C%20and%20I%20do%20the%20same%20with%20my%20team.%20I%20put%20my%20team%20members'%20vacations%20in%20my%20calendar%20as%20all-day%20events%20to%20ensure%20I%20don't%20call%2C%20text%2C%20or%20email%20them.%20Time%20off%20to%20recharge%20drives%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20doing%20something%20client-related%2C%20such%20as%20dinner%20meetings%2C%20several%20nights%20a%20week.%20I'm%20also%20part%20of%20a%20civic%20group%20and%20several%20charity%20boards%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20events%20a%20few%20nights%20a%20week.%20On%20the%20nights%20I'm%20not%20going%20out%2C%20I'm%20also%20going%20through%20some%20emails%20and%20pre-reads%20for%20the%20next%20day's%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20will%20have%20an%20IPA%2C%20preferably%20a%20Logboat%20Snapper%2C%20a%20great%20Missouri%20brand.%20I%20usually%20drink%20nonalcoholic%20beer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20throttle%20down%20around%208%3A30%20or%209%20p.m.%20I%20watch%20a%20streaming%20series%2C%20sports%2C%20or%20read.%20We%20stream%20a%20lot%2C%20as%20I'm%20a%20massive%20fan%20of%20most%20genres%20(excluding%20horror).%20Sports%20documentaries%20are%20some%20of%20my%20favorites%2C%20but%20I%