ofit-rises-to-rs-60-22-cr-revenue-up-9-125012800802_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Malaysia-U.K.%20Rom-Com%20%E2%80%98Mojo%E2%80%99%20Unveils%20Cast%2C%20Astro%20Shaw%20Boards%20as%20Co-Producer%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738058400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FMojo-collage.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236288365%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Malaysian%20powerhouse%20Astro%20Shaw%20has%20joined%20forces%20with%20Sympatico%2C%20the%20newly%20minted%20production%20label%20from%20Double%20Vision%E2%80%99s%20Min%20Lim%20and%20Argo%20Films%E2%80%99%20Richard%20Johns%2C%20as%20the%20outfit%20commences%20production%20on%20its%20debut%20feature%20%E2%80%9CMojo.%E2%80%9D%20The%20romantic%20comedy%2C%20which%20began%20lensing%20this%20week%20in%20Malaysia%E2%80%99s%20picturesque%20Perlis%20region%2C%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20cross-cultural%20collaboration%20between%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fmalaysia-uk-rom-com-mojo-cast-astro-shaw-1236288365%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20India-China%20Grow%20Close%2C%20Who's%20Driving%20The%20'Narrative'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Foreign%20Secretary%2C%20Vikram%20Misri%2C%20was%20recently%20in%20China%20on%20a%20two-day%20trip%20to%20discuss%20the%20future%20course%20of%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20following%20an%20initiative%20by%20both%20nations%20to%20normalise%20ties%20after%20a%20military%20standoff%20spanning%20nearly%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Host%20Of%20Measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20were%20fraught%20after%20Beijing%20unilaterally%20tried%20to%20change%20the%20status%20quo%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%202020%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20soldiers%20on%20both%20sides.%20As%20a%20response%20to%20China's%20military%20coercion%20and%20amassing%20troops%20along%20the%20border%2C%20New%20Delhi%20responded%20by%20adopting%20a%20stringent%20position%2C%20that%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20along%20the%20boundary%20would%20decide%20the%20overall%20relationship.%20This%20approach%20necessitated%20viewing%20trade%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20interactions%20from%20a%20national%20security%20lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20nearly%20300%20Chinese%20mobile%20applications%20were%20banned%2C%20direct%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20were%20halted%2C%20strict%20curbs%20were%20imposed%20on%20visas%20for%20Chinese%20nationals%2C%20and%20educational%20cooperation%20between%20universities%20was%20reviewed.%20In%20October%202024%2C%20both%20nations%20finalised%20patrolling%20arrangements%20for%20friction%20points%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20following%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20met%20at%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Russia.%20This%20resumption%20of%20top-level%20engagement%20has%20been%20followed%20by%20regular%20meetings%20down%20the%20hierarchy%20to%20chart%20the%20future%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20On%20Trade%2C%20Economy%2C%20And%20People%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20disengagement%20having%20been%20completed%20and%20the%20resumption%20of%20patrolling%20as%20per%20the%20respective%20perceptions%20of%20the%20border%2C%20the%20focus%20has%20shifted%20to%20aspects%20like%20economic%20engagement%20and%20people-to-people%20ties%2C%20which%20had%20been%20in%20a%20deep%20freeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restarting%20of%20the%20Special%20Representatives%20(SRs)%20mechanism%2C%20which%20was%20tasked%20with%20ways%20to%20settle%20the%20boundary%20question%20from%20a%20political%20perspective%20under%20an%20agreement%20in%202003%2C%20is%20a%20welcome%20move.%20Besides%2C%20the%20Indian%20readout%20of%20Misri's%20trip%20states%20that%20the%20pilgrimage%20to%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20in%20Tibet%20will%20resume%20this%20year.%20The%20meeting%20of%20the%20expert%20panel%20to%20confer%20on%20the%20resumption%20of%20sharing%20of%20hydrological%20data%20and%20cooperation%20on%20transnational%20rivers%20has%20been%20advanced.%20Interactions%20between%20media%20outlets%20and%20think%20tanks%20are%20set%20to%20resume.%20The%20pathway%20to%20restart%20direct%20air%20services%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20also%20being%20cleared.%20There%20is%20also%20an%20impetus%20to%20address%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20economy%20and%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20All%20Is%20Well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20challenges%20remain%20and%20overshadow%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20while%20disengagement%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20the%20weaponry%20assembled%20along%20the%20border%20during%20the%20standoff%20remains%20in%20place.%20This%20raises%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20disengagement%20has%20been%20a%20tactical%20move%20for%20the%20Chinese.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20Day%2C%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20cautioned%20that%20while%20the%20conditions%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20were%20stable%20but%20sensitive%2C%20both%20armies%20were%20locked%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdegree%20of%20standoff%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20in%20earlier%20rounds%20in%202022%2C%20disengagement%20was%20achieved%20at%20some%20points%20after%20creating%20no-patrol%20zones.%20While%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20temporary%20measure%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20how%20long%20these%20no-go%20areas%20for%20both%20militaries%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20while%20military%20tensions%20are%20down%2C%20the%20strategy%20of%20cartographic%20warfare%20and%20weaponising%20of%20natural%20resources%20continues.%20Beijing%20recently%20announced%20plans%20to%20carve%20out%20two%20counties%2C%20which%20subsume%20a%20part%20of%20the%20territory%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20in%20Xinjiang%20province's%20Hotan%20prefecture.%20It%20is%20also%20constructing%20the%20world's%20biggest%20hydroelectric%20project%20on%20the%20Yarlung%20Zangbo%20river%20in%20Tibet%20(referred%20to%20as%20Brahmaputra%20after%20it%20enters%20Arunachal%20Pradesh).%20New%20Delhi%20has%20conveyed%20its%20concerns%20to%20Beijing%20on%20both%20these%20developments%20through%20diplomatic%20channels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarrative%20Games%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20trust%20and%20peace.%20Going%20further%2C%20China's%20use%20of%20non-conventional%20means%20to%20gain%20leverage%20over%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20queer%20the%20pitch%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20a%20settlement.%20New%20Delhi%20needs%20to%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20narratives%20emanating%20from%20Beijing's%20strategic%20class.%20Their%20notion%20is%20that%20India%20is%20conciliating%20with%20China%20from%20a%20position%20of%20vulnerability.%20Second%2C%20they%20believe%20that%20India's%20relenting%20in%20imposing%20restrictions%20on%20Chinese%20corporations%20was%20hurting%20the%20Indian%20economy%20more.%20This%20sentiment%20has%20been%20buttressed%20ever%20since%20the%20Finance%20Ministry's%20Economic%20Survey%202023-24%20made%20a%20case%20for%20inviting%20Chinese%20capital%20and%20integrating%20into%20Chinese-led%20international%20value%20chains.%20Lastly%2C%20there%20are%20assumptions%20in%20Beijing%20that%20there%20is%20a%20degree%20of%20strategic%20mistrust%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%20in%20light%20of%20recent%20standoffs%20over%20the%20Pannun%20and%20Nijjar%20cases%2C%20and%20that%20this%20could%20force%20New%20Delhi%20to%20look%20towards%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Xi's%20bid%20to%20redraw%20boundaries%20may%20have%20failed%2C%20China%20is%20unlikely%20to%20stop%20poking%20around%20on%20sensitive%20issues%20through%20all%20such%20non-conventional%20means%2C%20and%20this%20can%20test%20New%20Delhi's%20cautious%20normalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V%20Pant%20is%20Vice%20President%2C%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20Kalpit%20Mankikar%20is%20Fellow%2C%20China%20Studies%2C%20at%20ORF.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738057980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-05%2Fxi-jinping-reuters_650x400_41494927275.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-china-are-growing-closer-but-look-out-for-narratives-7578052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Xis%20bid%20to%20redraw%20boundaries%20may%20have%20failed%2C%20China%20is%20unlikely%20to%20stop%20poking%20around%20on%20sensitive%20issues.%20And%20this%20can%20test%20India's%20cautious%20normalisation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-china-are-growing-closer-but-look-out-for-narratives-7578052%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Richa%20slams%20stereotypical%20depictions%20of%20'progressive'%20women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738057843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117628690%2Cimgsize-18714.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fricha-chadha-slams-stereotypical-depictions-of-progressive-women-in-bollywood%2Farticleshow%2F117628690.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left