0statement%20in%20the%20comments%20section.%20The%20company%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20sincerely%20apologize%20for%20the%20unfortunate%20incident%20of%20delivering%20a%20non-vegetarian%20burger%20to%20you.%20Our%20team%20recognized%20the%20error%20during%20your%20visit%20to%20our%20kitchen%20and%20expressed%20our%20regret%20for%20the%20mix-up%20at%20our%20dispatch%20station.%20Please%20be%20assured%20that%20we%20have%20taken%20this%20matter%20very%20seriously.%20Disciplinary%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20the%20responsible%20team%20members%2C%20and%20we%20have%20retrained%20our%20staff%20to%20ensure%20strict%20adherence%20to%20our%20processes%20moving%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20Menu%20also%20addressed%20the%20concerns%20raised%20about%20the%20location%20of%20the%20kitchen%20shown%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20clarify%20that%20our%20facility%20follows%20all%20required%20food%20safety%20measures%20within%20our%20premises.%20While%20we%20have%20been%20operating%20from%20this%20location%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20as%20tenants%2C%20our%20influence%20over%20the%20external%20environment%20is%20limited.%20However%2C%20we%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20we%20do%20not%20contribute%20negatively%20to%20the%20neighbourhood.%20We%20follow%20proper%20garbage%20and%20waste%20management%20practices.%20The%20water%20seen%20on%20the%20street%20originates%20from%20water%20tankers%20that%20service%20businesses%20and%20residential%20buildings%20in%20the%20morning%20hours%20and%20is%20not%20sewage.%20The%20lane%20is%20shared%20with%20nearly%2025%20other%20businesses%20and%20shops.%20Taking%20your%20feedback%20into%20account%2C%20we%20will%20actively%20collaborate%20with%20other%20businesses%20to%20improve%20the%20overall%20upkeep%20of%20the%20area.%20We%20value%20your%20feedback%20and%20deeply%20regret%20any%20inconvenience%20caused.%20Your%20concerns%20are%20important%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20a%20better%20experience%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20comments%20section%2C%20Instagram%20users%20were%20alarmed%20by%20the%20viral%20video.%20Read%20some%20of%20the%20reactions%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20I%20always%20check%20their%20ratings%20and%20photos%20on%20Google%20Maps%20and%20then%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFresh%20unhygienic%20menu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZomato%20should%20put%20outside-inside%20photos%20of%20all%20online%20restaurants%20on%20their%20app.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20order%20online%20from%20an%20unknown%20eatery.%20I%20always%20make%20sure%20to%20check%20online%20first.%20Gmap%20review%20and%20photos%20help%20me%20make%20the%20decision%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExactly%20the%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20me%202%20days%20back.%20Ordered%20a%20paneer%20burger%20and%20received%20a%20chicken%20burger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20thought%20this%20place%20had%20a%20hygienic%20professional%20kitchen%20run%20by%20chefs.%20Never%20ordering%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20usually%20order%20from%20restaurants%20I%20know%20or%20I%20have%20been%20to.%20I%20once%20had%20ordered%20from%20a%20new%20place%20and%20they%20sent%20the%20biryani%20in%20a%20plastic%20%3Cem%3Etheli%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20a%20spoon%20stuffed%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20Reddit%20post%20about%20a%20Fresh%20Menu%20customer%20allegedly%20finding%20a%20cockroach%20in%20their%20sandwich%20went%20viral.%20Click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Fnews%2Fviral-now-reddit-user-in-bengaluru-posts-about-finding-cockroach-in-sandwich-ordered-via-zomato-5282282%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20read%20the%20full%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw