20realistic%20without%20deep%20cuts%20to%20crucial%20social%20services%20or%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Festablishing-and-implementing-the-presidents-department-of-government-efficiency%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%2020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20White%20House%20announced%20that%20the%20United%20States%20Digital%20Service%20is%20being%20publicly%20renamed%20as%20the%20United%20States%20DOGE%20Service%20(USDS)%20and%20shall%20be%20established%20in%20the%20Executive%20Office%20of%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738055340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0m83vne_musk-trump-reuters_625x300_13_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fno-office-for-elon-musk-in-white-house-clarifies-donald-trump-7577910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20asked%20if%20Musk%20has%20an%20office%20in%20the%20West%20Wing%2C%20the%20President%20categorically%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20no%2C%20not%20-%20it's%20not%20Elon's%20office.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fno-office-for-elon-musk-in-white-house-clarifies-donald-trump-7577910%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Like%20any%20millennial%2C%20Yahoo%20wants%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20cool%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yahoo%20logo%20wears%20sunglasses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793b8f3ae09223df2bb6048%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EYahoo!%3B%20Chelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYahoo%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20platform%20once%20adored%20by%20Gen%20Xers%20and%20millennials%20a