%2Frefurbished-iphones-market-apple-sales-slump-android-cell-phones-cheaper-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20to%20its%20iPhone%2016%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20met%20with%20a%20shrug%20from%20consumers.%20As%20all%20these%20companies%20push%20for%20the%20future%2C%20Yahoo%20is%20marketing%20itself%20as%20a%20relic%20of%20a%20time%20when%20the%20internet%20was%20fun%20and%20full%20of%20opportunities%20for%20discovery%20but%20also%20signaling%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20generative-AI%20future.%20That's%20its%20challenge%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20very%20fragmented%20world%20where%20the%20algorithms%20maybe%20pushed%20everyone%20deeper%20into%20the%20things%20that%20they're%20reacting%20to%20most%2C%20how%20do%20you%20bring%20back%20the%20best%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20find%20those%20serendipitous%20or%20delightful%20moments%20mixed%20in%20with%20the%20stuff%20that%20we%20know%20you%20need%20to%20know%20or%20we%20know%20are%20going%20to%20help%20you%20accomplish%20your%20goals%20today%3F%26quot%3B%20Sanchez%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20pioneering%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20Yahoo%20became%20a%20media%20company%20more%20than%20a%20tech%20company.%20While%20everyone%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20building%20their%20own%20AI%2C%20Yahoo's%20approach%20is%20different.%20Its%20tools%20are%20built%20on%20large%20language%20models%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20Google%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20open-source%20LLMs%2C%20Sanchez%20tells%20me%2C%20while%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20even%20Musk's%20xAI%20are%20building%20LLMs.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bsupercharge%26quot%3B%20Yahoo's%20functions%2C%20he%20says%2C%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20summarize%20sporting%20events%20or%20organize%20unwieldy%20inboxes.%20That%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20to%20the%20company.%20%26quot%3BYahoo%20can%20be%20cool%20by%20making%20its%20search%20engine%20more%20conversational%2C%20assistive%2C%20and%20agentic%2C%26quot%3B%20Nikhil%20Lai%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Forrester%20Research%2C%20says%20in%20an%20email.%20More%20than%20one-third%20of%20people%20are%20using%20these%20conversational%20features%20to%20search%20%26quot%3Bwhenever%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Lai%20says%2C%20citing%20data%20from%20Forrester's%20Market%20Research%20Online%20Community.%20In%20addition%20to%20traditional%20search%2C%20Yahoo's%20search%20has%20an%20AI-powered%20chatbot%20designed%20to%20work%20much%20like%20ChatGPT%20or%20Perplexity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20date%20the%20platform%2C%20and%20myself%2C%20I%20probably%20last%20used%20my%20Yahoo%20email%20to%20apply%20to%20colleges%20in%202012%2C%20and%20it's%20since%20become%20a%20repository%20for%20promotional%20emails%20from%20companies%20I%20rarely%20shop%20from.%20For%20all%20the%20nostalgia%20Yahoo%20is%20playing%20up%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20company%20moving%20to%20add%20AI%20into%20its%20various%20apps%2C%20tech%20that%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20hype%20with%20yet-to-be-realized%20returns.%20The%20nudges%20to%20the%20'90s%20don't%20mean%20the%20company%20is%20actually%20moving%20backward%20to%20a%20young%20internet%20many%20long%20for.%20Those%20who%20come%20for%20the%20memories%20are%20going%20to%20find%20a%20very%20different%20Yahoo%20from%20the%20one%20they%20remember%20from%202005.%20But%20in%20the%20Big%20Tech%20landscape%20of%202025%2C%20Yahoo%20might%20not%20need%20to%20be%20cool%20to%20succeed%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20needs%20to%20be%20useful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies