ludes%20the%20Welsh%20government%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20which%20in%202022%20launched%20the%20first%20guaranteed-basic-income%20pilot%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20program%2C%20called%20Basic%20Income%20for%20Care%20Leavers%2C%20gave%20638%20young%20adults%20leaving%20the%20foster-care%20or%20local%20authority-care%20system%20a%20monthly%20payment%20of%20about%20%C2%A31%2C280%2C%20or%20%241%2C580%2C%20after%20taxes%20that%20they%20could%20spend%20on%20whatever%20they%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20is%20set%20to%20wrap%20up%20this%20year%2C%20and%20its%20results%20could%20inform%20a%20controversial%20debate%20in%20the%20UK%20over%20basic%20income.%20Guaranteed%20basic%20income%20offers%20recurring%20cash%20payments%20for%20a%20set%20period%20of%20time%20to%20a%20specific%20group%20of%20people%2C%20like%20mothers%20or%20artists.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20provides%20recurring%20cash%20payments%20to%20all%20people%20in%20a%20population%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20socioeconomic%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-with-universal-basic-income%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECountries%20testing%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20include%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Kenya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-pros-and-cons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupporters%20of%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20argue%20that%20it%20can%20address%20growing%20inequality%20and%20insulate%20workers%20from%20economic%20recessions%20and%20technological%20advances%20like%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20while%20opponents%20are%20concerned%20that%20basic%20income%20disincentives%20work%20and%20that%20programs%20are%20too%20expensive%20to%20implement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20experimentation%20going%20on%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20familiarity%20within%20policy%20circles%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20quite%20a%20controversial%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jack%20Kellam%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Autonomy%20Institute%2C%20a%20UK%20think%20tank%20that%20studies%20how%20to%20reshape%20work%20to%20address%20modern%20crises.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20people%20are%20cautious%20about%20touching%20it%20within%20mainstream%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20half%20the%202%2C233%20Britons%20in%20a%20July%20YouGov%20survey%20said%20they%20supported%20the%20idea%20of%20introducing%20UBI%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20while%20one-third%20opposed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ce9bab4-a35d-4685-b89f-4dc51ad73963%5C%22%3EHurdles%20for%20basic%20income%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20arguments%20against%20basic%20income%20is%20the%20price%20tag.%20Estimates%20of%20the%20cost%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20wide-ranging.%20A%20Georgetown%20University%20study%20published%20in%202023%20found%20that%20implementing%20UBI%20in%20the%20country%20would%20cost%20about%20%C2%A345%20billion%20a%20year%2C%20or%202%25%20of%20its%20GDP.%20A%20working%20paper%20by%20the%20Institute%20for%20Policy%20Research%20in%202017%20estimated%20it%20would%20cost%20more%20than%20%C2%A3427%20billion%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmaller%20guaranteed-basic-income%20programs%20can%20be%20easier%20to%20implement.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Welsh%20government%20allocated%20about%20%C2%A320%20million%20over%20three%20years%20for%20its%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20hasn't%20been%20without%20controversy.%20The%20UK%20government%2C%20which%20in%202022%20was%20controlled%20by%20the%20Conservative%20Party%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fsocial-policy-and-society%2Farticle%2Fdevolution-and-social-citizenship-the-case-of-the-basic-income-pilot-for-care-leavers-in-wales%2F0DC73C2F7CD3DE275E5CD39F206385C4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopposed%20the%20Wales%20pilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20UBI%20would%20discourage%20work%20and%20require%20significant%20tax%20increases%20to%20fund.%20Britain's%20Labour%20Party%20swept%20to%20power%20in%20July%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20has%20previously%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20attracted%26quot%3B%20to%20UBI%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20response%20to%20advances%20in%20AI.%20He%20said%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20retraining%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Labour%20Party%20also%20controls%20the%20Welsh%20Parliament%2C%20but%20Kellam%20said%20that%20in%20Wales%20the%20party%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20progressive%20than%20its%20national%20counterpart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Autonomy%20Institute%20in%202023%20proposed%20its%20own%20basic-income%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fautonomy.work%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2FBASINC.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicropilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20UK%20for%2015%20people%2C%20but%20Kellam%20said%20it%20hadn't%20attracted%20a%20funder%20yet.%20He%20hopes%20the%20results%20of%20the%20pilot%20in%20Wales%2C%20as%20well%20as%20emerging%20research%20in%20the%20US%20indicating%20the%20success%20of%20similar%20pilots%2C%20will%20create%20some%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fguaranteedincome.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2030%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-united-states%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic-income%20pilots%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eby%20the%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Pilots%20Dashboard%20%E2%80%94%20a%20research%20group%20that%20visualizes%20data%20from%20the%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20involving%20nearly%208%2C500%20participants%20found%20more%20than%20half%20the%20cash%20grants%20went%20toward%20food%20and%20groceries%2C%20transportation%2C%20housing%2C%20utilities%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education.%20Smaller%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-basic-income-study-results-starting-a-business-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic-income%20studies%20and%20experiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20cash%20payments%20helped%20participants%20earn%20higher%20wages%2C%20boosted%20job%20satisfaction%2C%20and%20improved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-carbon-taxes-global-gdp-sustainability-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKellam%20said%20another%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eobstacle%20to%20implementing%20basic%20income%20in%20the%20UK%20is%20the%20government's%20centralized%20structure%2C%20which%20thwarts%20local%20leaders'%20ability%20to%20launch%20their%20own%20basic%20income%20pilots%2C%20like%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20US%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20trials%20are%20taking%20place%20at%20the%20town%20and%20city%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Kellam%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20lack%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20UK.%20We're%20involved%20in%20some%20of%20the%20discussions%20at%20local%20councils.%20But%20it's%20seen%20as%20less%20politically%20contagious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi-uk%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738054982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f439196626c40984f988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi-uk%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Universal%20basic%20income%20is%20politically%20controversial%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20but%20the%20Wales%20government%20is%20testing%20a%20small%20pilot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%