s%20still%20a%20fraction%20of%20OpenAI's%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20translates%2C%20as%20company%20boss%20Sam%20Altman%20pointed%20out%2C%20into%20significantly%20enhanced%20computing%20capabilities%2C%20but%20for%20the%20DeepSeek%20model%20to%20deliver%20at%20least%20that%20much%20processing%20power%20on%20its%20relatively%20shoestring%20budget%20is%20an%20eyebrow-raiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Mr%20Altman%20acknowledged%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeepseeks-r1-is-an-impressive-model-says-openai-chief-sam-altman-7575749%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalling%20the%20R1%20model%20%26quot%3Bvery%20impressive%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20boss%20Sundar%20Pichai%20went%20one%20step%20further%2C%20telling%20CNBC%20at%20Davos%2C%20%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20we%20should%20take%20the%20development%20out%20of%20China%20very%20seriously.%26quot%3B%20And%20US%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-wake-up-call-for-us-says-donald-trump-on-chinas-deepseek-ai-7575054%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%20sounded%20a%20%26quot%3Bwake-up%26quot%3B%20call%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20are%20the%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20that%20US%20companies%20have%20lost%20amid%20a%20rout%20this%20week%20in%20tech%20stocks%3B%20chip-maker%20Nvidia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20lost%20over%20%24600%20billion%20and%20the%20tech-rich%20Nasdaq%20index%20finished%20Monday%20down%20by%20more%20than%20three%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20the%20unwelcome%20possibility%20of%20a%20further%20drop%20based%20on%20AI%20giants%20Meta%20and%20Microsoft's%20expected%20earnings%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnvidia-loses-nearly-600-billion-as-chinas-deepseek-jolts-tech-shares-7575388%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20Loses%20Nearly%20%24600%2