3E%26quot%3BAmmonia%20levels%20continue%20to%20be%206%20times%20above%20normal%20in%20Yamuna%20waters%2C%20at%20the%20point%20it%20is%20entering%20Delhi%20from%20Haryana.%20Such%20levels%20are%20extremely%20toxic%20for%20the%20human%20body.%20This%20water%20cannot%20be%20treated%20and%20supplied%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20Otherwise%2C%20their%20lives%20will%20be%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20had%20denied%20the%20AAP's%20charges%20and%20threatened%20them%20with%20a%20defamation%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20said%20in%20her%20letter%20that%20the%20water%20treatment%20plants%20belonging%20to%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20can%20treat%20ammonia%20up%20to%201%20ppm%20level%20but%20ammonia%20levels%20in%20the%20water%20coming%20from%20Haryana%20to%20Delhi%20are%20700%25%20above%20the%20treatable%20limit.%20This%20has%20curtailed%20the%20water%20supply%20in%20the%20city%20by%2015-20%25%2C%20she%20said%2C%20warning%20that%20high%20levels%20of%20ammonia%20in%20drinking%20water%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20public%20health%20crisis%20and%20cause%20kidney%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20an%20act%20of%20negligence%3B%20it%20is%20an%20act%20of%20water%20terrorism%20to%20deliberately%20impact%20the%20conduct%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20alleged%20yesterday%20the%20BJP%20resorted%20to%20such%20a%20drastic%20step%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20losing%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Hinduism%2C%20there%20is%20no%20bigger%20sin%20than%20stopping%20water.%20The%20people%20of%20Delhi%20will%20answer%20the%20BJP%20for%20this%20sin%20on%20February%205%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%2C%20added%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20keep%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20thirsty%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bdirty%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20nothing%20could%20be%20more%20disgusting%20than%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20poison%20that%20is%20being%20mixed%20in%20water%20and%20sent%20cannot%20even%20be%20cleaned%20in%20the%20water%20treatment%20plant.%20For%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%20water%20supply%20has%20to%20be%20stopped%20in%20many%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20AAP%20boss%20who%20has%20promised%20to%20return%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20his%20party%20wins%20the%20February%205%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20charges%2C%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20has%20demanded%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20apologise%20or%20they%20will%20sue%20him.%20%26quot%3BFor%20these%20blatantly%20false%20and%20disgusting%20statements%2C%20Kejriwal%20should%20immediately%20apologise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%20for%20this%20statement%2C%20otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20file%20a%20defamation%20suit%20against%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20today%2C%20Haryana%20Minister%20Mahipal%20Dhanda%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bunsubstantiated%20claim%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bobjectionable%20and%20dangerous%20statement%20full%20of%20agenda%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20AAP%20chief%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20mere%20apology%20won't%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20too%20has%20accused%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20of%20lying%20with%20party%20candidate%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%20saying%20he%20is%20surprised%20that%20no%20action%20is%20being%20taken%20against%20him%20by%20Haryana%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738052400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fgp0pfq08_atishi-nayab-saini-_625x300_28_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-doubles-down-on-yamuna-poisoning-charge-against-haryana-says-water-supply-hit-7576840%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20acc