%20as%20South%20African%20icon%20AB%20de%20Villiers%20announces%20his%20long-awaited%20return%20to%20the%20sport%20after%20nearly%20four%20years.%20De%20Villiers%2C%20revered%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20and%20electrifying%20cricketers%20of%20all%20time%2C%20will%20lead%20the%20Game%20Changers%20South%20Africa%20Champions%20in%20the%20second%20edition%20of%20the%20World%20Championship%20of%20Legends%20(WCL).%20This%20premier%20T20%20tournament%2C%20featuring%20retired%20and%20non-contracted%20cricket%20legends%2C%20promises%20a%20nostalgic%20yet%20exhilarating%20spectacle%20for%20fans%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20return%2C%20de%20Villiers%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFour%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20retired%20from%20all%20cricket%20because%20I%20just%20didn't%20feel%20the%20urge%20to%20play%20any%20more.%20Well%2C%20time%20has%20passed%2C%20and%20my%20young%20sons%20have%20started%20playing%20the%20game.%20We've%20been%20playing%20more%20and%20more%20often%20in%20the%20garden%2C%20and%2C%20well%2C%20it%20feels%20as%20though%20some%20kind%20of%20flame%20has%20been%20lit%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20quoted%20from%20a%20release%20by%20WCL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20am%20heading%20back%20to%20the%20gym%20and%20the%20nets%2C%20and%20I'll%20be%20ready%20for%20WCL%20in%20July%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20unmatched%20versatility%20and%20fearless%20batting%2C%20de%20Villiers'%20comeback%20has%20ignited%20excitement%20within%20the%20cricketing%20fraternity.%20The%20Game%20Changers%20squad%2C%20which%20featured%20legends%20such%20as%20Jacques%20Kallis%2C%20Herschelle%20Gibbs%2C%20Dale%20Steyn%2C%20and%20Imran%20Tahir%20in%20the%20inaugural%20season%2C%20now%20has%20an%20even%20brighter%20future%20under%20de%20Villiers'%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmandeep%20Singh%20%2C%20Co-Owner%20of%20South%20Africa%20Champions%20%26amp%3B%20Founder%20of%20Game%20Changers%20shared%20his%20excitement%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20honoured%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20World%20Championship%20of%20Legends%20and%20showcase%20the%20incredible%20talent%20of%20our%20cricketing%20greats.%20AB%20de%20Villiers'%20return%20as%20our%20captain%20is%20a%20monumental%20boost%20for%20our%20team%2C%20and%20his%20leadership%20will%20undoubtedly%20inspire%20us%20to%20new%20heights%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarry%20Singh%2C%20Co-Owner%20of%20South%20Africa%20Champions%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAB%20de%20Villiers%20is%20not%20just%20a%20player%3B%20he's%20an%20icon%20who%20has%20inspired%20millions%20around%20the%20world.%20His%20decision%20to%20lead%20our%20team%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20love%20for%20the%20game%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't%20be%20more%20thrilled%20to%20have%20him%20on%20board.%20This%20marks%20a%20historic%20moment%20for%20the%20team%20and%20the%20league%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20quoted%20from%20a%20release%20by%20WCL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20Tomar%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20World%20Championship%20of%20Legends%2C%20expressed%20his%20enthusiasm%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20precisely%20why%20we%20launched%20the%20WCL%20-%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20legends%20we%20deeply%20miss.%20As%20a%20fan%20of%20AB%20de%20Villiers%2C%20I'm%20thrilled%20to%20see%20him%20return%20to%20the%20field.%20I'm%20sure%20cricket%20lovers%20in%20England%20and%20beyond%20will%20be%20delighted%20by%20his%20comeback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishant%20Pitti%2C%20Chief%20Patron%20of%20the%20WCL%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20partnership%20with%20the%20World%20Championship%20of%20Legends%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20cricket's%20golden%20era.%20The%20return%20of%20AB%20de%20Villiers%20embodies%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20league%2C%20and%20we%20are%20privileged%20to%20witness%20this%20iconic%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738048920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F35ghp28o_ab-de-villiers-bcci_625x300_24_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fab-de-villiers-returns-to-cricket-all-set-to-feature-as-captain-in-7576771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricketing%20fans%20worldwide%20are%20set%20to%20celebrate%20as%20South%20African%20icon%20AB%20de%20Villiers%20announces%20his%20long-awaited%20return%20to%20the%20sport%20after%20nearly%20four%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Drill%2C%20Baby%2C%20Drill%3A%20Will%20Trump's%20'Emergency'%20Plan%20To%20Make%20Oil%20Cheap%20Work%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20assuming%20office%2C%20laid%20out%20a%20sweeping%20plan%20to%20maximise%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%2C%20including%20declaring%20a%20national%20energy%20emergency%20to%20speed%20the%20permitting%20of%20projects%2C%20rolling%20back%20environmental%20protections%2C%20suspending%20new%20federal%20offshore%20wind%20leasing%20proposals%20pending%20an%20environmental%20and%20economic%20review%2C%20and%20withdrawing%20the%20US%20from%20the%20Paris%20climate%20pact.%20He%20also%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20reversing%20efforts%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20restrict%20oil%20and%20gas%20drilling%20in%20the%20Arctic%20and%20large%20areas%20of%20the%20US%20coastline.%20This%20is%20a%20dramatic%20U-turn%20in%20Washington's%20energy%20policy%20after%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20during%20his%20four%20years%20in%20office%20encouraged%20a%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20to%20clean%20energy%20in%20the%20world's%20largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20said%20in%20his%20inaugural%20address%2C%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20will%20be%20a%20manufacturing%20nation%3Cbr%3E%5Cnonce%20again%2C%20and%20we%20have%20something%20that%20no%20other%20manufacturing%20nation%20will%20ever%20have%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20amount%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20of%20any%20country%20on%20earth%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20use%20it.%20We%20will%20bring%20prices%20down%2C%20fill%20our%20strategic%20reserves%20up%20again%20right%20to%20the%20top%2C%20and%20export%20American%20energy%20all%20over%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrude%20oil%20is%20produced%20in%2032%20states%20in%20the%20US%20and%20its%20coastal%20waters.%20Texas%20is%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20oil-producing%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20In%202023%2C%20it%20produced%20a%20total%20of%20over%202%20billion%20barrels.%20Its%20%24172-billion%20energy%20sector%20employed%20more%20than%209%20lakh%20energy%20workers%20as%20of%202022.%20President%20Trump%20has%20already%20started%20pushing%20for%20an%20increase%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%20to%20lower%20energy%20costs%20and%20drive%20prices%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20all%20as%20simple%20as%20it%20sounds%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%20Is%20King%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20incentive%20for%20oil%20and%20gas%20firms%20to%20either%20stimulate%20oil%20production%20or%20curtail%20it%20is%20usually%20price.%20In%20general%2C%20high%20oil%20prices%20push%20oil%20companies%20to%20produce%20more%2C%20while%20low%20prices%20lead%20them%20to%20pull%20back.%20The%20government%20has%20limited%20power%20to%20affect%20the%20price%20of%20oil%20as%20it%20is%20controlled%20by%20market%20dynamics.%20Higher%20prices%20may%20lead%20to%20more%20production%2C%20but%20they%20also%20upset%20consumers%20who%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20pay%20more%20at%20the%20pump%2C%20which%20will%20make%20not%20only%20gas%20but%20other%20commodities%20costlier.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20oil%20companies%20have%20resisted%20the%20temptation%20to%20significantly%20invest%20in%20expanding%20drilling%20when%20prices%20rise%2C%20embracing%20instead%20the%20ability%20to%20sell%20their%20oil%20for%20a%20high%20price.%20Not%20all%20oil%20reserves%20can%20be%20exploited%20profitably.%20Instead%20of%20drilling%20at%20new%20locations%2C%20many%20oil%20companies%20have%20focused%20on%20extracting%20every%20dollar%20from%20existing%20wells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20be%20a%20solution%20then%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Is%20An%20Attractive%20Destination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20may%20lie%20in%20the%20export%20of%20products%20such%20as%20Liquefied%20Natural%20Gas%20(LNG).%20President%20Trump%20understands%20this%20well%2C%20and%20has%20thus%20lifted%20the%20previous%20administration's%20freeze%20on%20export%20permits.%20The%20decision%20could%20lead%20to%20almost%20100%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20per%20annum%20(MTPA)%20of%20additional%20LNG%20being%20exported%20by%202031%20by%20projects%20that%20are%20significantly%20advanced%2C%20further%20cementing%20the%20US%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20exporter%20of%20the%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Senator%20Ted%20Cruz%20has%20also%20already%20introduced%20legislation%20to%20repeal%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20Natural%20Gas%20Tax%20in%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act.%20Rolling%20it%20back%20it%20is%20an%20important%20step%20towards%20ensuring%20affordable%2C%20reliable%20energy%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Shell's%20%3Cem%3ELNG%20Outlook%202024%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20global%20demand%20for%20LNG%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20by%20more%20than%2050%25%20by%202040.%20This%20will%20be%20driven%20largely%20by%20the%20move%20away%20from%20higher-emission%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20a%20shift%20underway%20in%20a%20large%20country%20such%20as%20India%20and%20further%20along%20in%20other%20emerging%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20China%20was%20the%20United%20States'%20largest%20oil%20export%20destination%2C%20while%20India%20stood%20fifth.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20the%20roles%20had%20reversed%2C%20with%20India%20taking%20the%20top%20spot%20and%20China%20going%20down%20to%20fifth.%20Various%20factors%20were%20responsible%2C%20including%20China%20imposing%20tariffs%20on%20US%20imports%2C%20the%20American%20ban%20on%20investments%20in%20Chinese%20energy%20firms%2C%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20LNG%20in%20India.%20A%20long-term%20contract%20worth%20%2410%20billion%20was%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20two%20LNG%20export%20terminals%20in%20Texas%20and%20Louisiana.%20There%20are%20more%20in%20the%20works%2C%20with%20Corpus%20Christi%20and%20Freeport%20in%20Texas%2C%20along%20with%20other%20Gulf%20Coast%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20A%20Complete%20Repeal%20Is%20Not%20Feasible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20executive%20order%20last%20week%2C%20Trump%20suspended%20funding%20disbursements%20under%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20(IRA)%2C%20a%20step%20part%20of%20a%20sweeping%20set%20of%20directives%20to%20begin%20setting%20the%20new%20administration's%20energy%20agenda.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20uncommon%20for%20new%20governments%20to%20pause%20funding%20for%20evaluation%2C%20federal%20agencies%20have%2090%20days%20to%20submit%20their%20review%20and%20spending%20recommendations%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20and%20the%20National%20Economic%20Council.%20The%20IRA%20contains%20key%20tax%20subsidies%20that%20foster%20energy%20production%20from%20renewable%20sources%20such%20as%20solar%2C%20hydrogen%2C%20wind%20and%20others.%20It%20also%20bolsters%20manufacturers%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20with%20incentives%20and%20investments.%20Renewable%20energy%20manufacturers%20are%20eligible%20for%20two%20federal%20tax%20credits%20under%20the%20IRA.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20IRA%20provides%20support%20for%20emerging%20capabilities%2C%20like%20carbon%20capture%20and%20technologies%20that%20facilitate%20the%20production%2C%20storage%20and%20utilisation%20of%20hydrogen%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20disbursements%20may%20be%20suspended%2C%20it%20is%20not%20prudent%20to%20repeal%20the%20law%20in%20its%20entirety%20for%20several%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20Red%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Texas%2C%20greatly%20benefit%20from%20it.%20In%20general%2C%20many%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20are%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20which%20usually%20send%20Republicans%20to%20Congress.%20For%20example%2C%20Texas%20has%20689%20firms%20engaged%20in%20solar%20manufacturing%20and%20distribution%2C%20with%20a%20%2445.2%20billion%20investment%20as%20of%20September%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Solar%20Energy%20Industries%20Association%20report.%20Thus%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20balance%20against%20the%20need%20to%20avoid%20rolling%20back%20the%20considerable%20stimulus%20the%20IRA%20provided%20to%20the%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20considerable%20foreign%20investment%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20in%20the%20US.%20Recently%2C%20an%20India-based%20solar%20panel%20maker%20established%20its%20first%20American%20solar%20module%20manufacturing%20and%20integrated%20US-made%20solar%20cell%20facility%20in%20Texas.%20The%20firm%20is%20planning%20to%20invest%20%241%20billion%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20next%20four%20years%20and%20create%20over%201%2C500%20jobs%20when%20at%20full%20capacity.%20There%20are%20several%20local%20firms%20engaged%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20and%20manufacturing%20of%20components%20needed%20for%20renewable%20energy%20production%20on%20the%20Gulf%20Coast.%20Most%20of%20these%20firms%20rely%20on%20a%20few%20benefits%20provided%20by%20the%20IRA%20to%20be%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20in%20the%20short%20term.%20Repealing%20it%20will%20discourage%20these%20firms%2C%20which%20have%20already%20invested%20or%20were%20planning%20to%20invest%20in%20renewables%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Need%20To%20Co-Exist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectricity%20demand%20continues%20to%20soar%20in%20America.%20The%20accelerated%20pace%20of%20modernisation%20in%20all%20sectors%2C%20from%20technology%20to%20transportation%20to%20heavy%20industry%2C%20needs%20electricity%20as%20a%20source%20of%20power.%20Crypto%20miners%20and%20data%20centres%2C%20are%20all%20heavy%20power%20consumers%2C%20as%20is%20generative%20AI%20technology%2C%20which%20demands%20immense%20computational%20power%20and%20energy%2C%20often%20ten%20times%20more%20than%20standard%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20are%20cost-competitive%20vis%20a%20vis%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20local%20utility%20providers%20may%20increasingly%20rely%20on%20them%20to%20meet%20the%20increasing%20demand.%20Another%20factor%20is%20that%20the%20prices%20of%20renewable%20energy%20are%20much%20less%20volatile%20than%20those%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20like%20natural%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20even%20with%20the%20shift%20in%20the%20US%20political%20climate%2C%20companies%2C%20and%20tech%20companies%20especially%2C%20can't%20completely%20abandon%20their%20commitment%20to%20all%20their%20stakeholders%E2%80%94employees%2C%20customers%2C%20and%20shareholders%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad%E2%80%94to%20make%20their%20operations%20sustainable.%20Currently%2C%2038%20states%20have%20regulations%20requiring%20utilities%20to%20obtain%20a%20certain%20percentage%20of%20their%20electricity%20from%20renewable%20sources.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20companies%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20direct%20purchasers%20of%20power%20from%20suppliers%2C%20bypassing%20intermediaries%20such%20as%20utility%20companies.%20This%20trend%20will%20support%20the%20demand%20for%20clean%20energy%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBottom%20Line%3A%20FDI%20Is%20Key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20huge%20potential%20for%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20in%20renewable%20energy%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20the%20export%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20to%20fast-growing%20countries%20such%20as%20India.%20It%20won't%20be%20surprising%20if%20President%20Trump%2C%20being%20the%20business-savvy%20leader%20he%20is%20with%20his%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20and%20%E2%80%9CMake%20in%20America%E2%80%9D%20vision%2C%20strikes%20a%20balance%20for%20the%20co-existence%20of%20both%20fossil%20fuels%20as%20well%20as%20renewable%20energy%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20%C7%AAuantAi%2C%20an%20investor%20in%20Private%20Equity%20and%20an%20advisory%20board%20member%20of%20several%20technology%20and%20non-profit%20firms%20in%20the%20US)%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738048320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fedata.ndtv.com%2Ffeeds%2Fliveblog%2F7514908%2F638730839432088929.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-trumps-plan-to-make-oil-cheaper-as-simple-as-it-sounds-7576878%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Trump%20has%20already%20started%20pushing%20for%20an%20increase%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%2C%20to%20lower%20energy%20costs%20and%20drive%20prices%20down.%20Is%20it%20all%20as%20simple%20as%20it%20sounds%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-trumps-plan-to-make-oil-cheaper-as-simple-as-it-sounds-7576878%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20DeepSeek%3F%20The%20low-cost%20Chinese%20AI%20firm%20that%20has%20turned%20the%20tech%20world%20upside%20down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738048200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F01%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-deepseek-app_6812411.jpg%3F20250128034509%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-is-deepseek-the-low-cost-chi