nk%5C%22%3Einterest%20in%20STEM%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Through%20competitions%20like%20the%20First%20Tech%20Challenge%20and%20Youth%20Climate%20Change%2C%20I%20gained%20recognition%20and%20confidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20TIS%20has%20impacted%20over%2010%2C500%20students%20and%20continues%20to%20grow.%20With%20centres%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Noida%2C%20Meenal%20looks%20ahead%20to%20guide%20one%20million%20children%20by%202030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20every%20child%20has%20the%20skills%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20mindset%20to%20change%20the%20world.%20When%20I%20see%20a%20child%20light%20up%20after%20building%20their%20first%20robot%2C%20or%20when%20they%20solve%20a%20problem%20they%20once%20thought%20was%20impossible%2C%20I%20know%20we%E2%80%99re%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Meenal%20Majumder%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737695273000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-08-at-13.00.30-1_11zon-1737181089.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D398871%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meenal%20Majumder%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20ICICI%20Securities%2C%20founded%20The%20Innovation%20Story%20(TIS)%20to%20provide%20project-based%20STEM%20education%20to%20children%20from%20underserved%20communities%20and%20private%20schools.%20TIS%20empowers%20young%20minds%20with%20skills%20in%20robotics%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20coding%2C%20bridging%20the%20digital%20divide%20and%20preparing%20them%20for%20future%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F398871%2Fmeenal-majumder-the-innovation-story-stem-education-project-learning-and-scholarships%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Women%20in%20UP%20%26amp%3B%20Bihar%20Are%20Defying%20Widowhood%2C%20Violence%2C%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Climate%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20shatter%20barriers%2C%20question%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20and%20inspire%20a%20wave%20of%20change%3F%20For%20countless%20women%20across%20India%20running%20small%20grassroots%20organisations%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mix%20of%20courage%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20an%20unshakable%20urge%20to%20address%20deep-rooted%20inequities%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20progress%20has%20been%20made%2C%20gender%20equality%20remains%20elusive.%20Women%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20and%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20continue%20to%20face%20entrenched%20barriers%20such%20as%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20social%20exclusion%2C%20and%20limited%20access%20to%20resources.%20At%20the%20current%20pace%2C%20it%20will%20take%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fpress%2F2023%2F06%2Fgender-equality-is-stalling-131-years-to-close-the-gap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E131%20years%20to%20achieve%20gender%20parity%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%20But%20this%20can%20change%20when%20women%20begin%20to%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMarriage%2C%20separation%2C%20and%20widowhood%20in%20rural%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20grassroots%2C%20early%20marriage%2C%20motherhood%2C%20widowhood%2C%20divorce%20or%20separation%20can%20be%20defining%20milestones%20for%20women%3B%20stepping%20away%20from%20the%20norm%20and%20reconstructing%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20identity%20post%20widowhood%20or%20separation%20is%20often%20an%20act%20of%20bold%20agency%2C%20and%20is%20pivotal%20for%20women%20working%20and%20enduring%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%20often%20having%20to%20relive%20personal%20trauma%20while%20supporting%20other%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERebuild%20is%20bringing%20to%20light%20how%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20often%20born%20from%20lived%20experience%20of%20violence%2C%20redefines%20power%20by%20focusing%20on%20collective%20contribution%2C%20building%20supportive%20communities%2C%20and%20dismantling%20existing%20structures%20that%20perpetuate%20violence%20and%20inequity.%20We%20are%20learning%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20not%20only%20empowers%20women%20and%20girls%20but%20also%20all%20marginalised%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20Navchetana%20Sarvangin%20Vikas%20Kendra%2C%20led%20by%20Manisha%20Sitaram%20Ghule%2C%20has%20made%20a%20profound%20impact.%20Operating%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20Beed%20district%2C%20the%20organisation%20focuses%20on%20advocacy%20for%20land%20rights%20and%20menstrual%20health%20for%20vulnerable%20nomadic%20and%20de-notified%20tribes%2C%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20they%20have%20enabled%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20loans%20from%20banks%2C%20helping%20women%20members%20build%20sustainable%20livelihoods.%20Their%20community%20dairy%20initiative%20is%20enabling%20enhanced%20incomes%2C%20ending%20migration%20for%20work%2C%20and%20bettering%20nutritional%20outcomes%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20512px)%20100vw%2C%20512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manisha%20Sitaram%20Ghule%20started%20a%20dairy%20initiative%20in%20Beed%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010.jpg%20512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3